  "title": "最小二乘法",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; white-space: normal;\"><del style=\"position:relative;display:block;z-index:10;\"><a  style=\"position: absolute;color: #FFF;text-decoration: none;font-size: 12px;height: 25px;border-radius: 0;margin-top: -20px;right: 15px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border-left: 10px solid #BB3A34;border-right: 10px solid #BB3A34;border-bottom: 5px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width: 0;text-indent:-100000px;\" href=\"http://maxiang.io/#/?provider=evernote&amp;guid=32a578bd-b547-4ce0-81a5-a83c24bc4fb1&amp;notebook=%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E6%9C%AC\">Edit</a></del><div  style=\"color: #2c3f51; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', SimSun, Song, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                        \n                    \n\n\n\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 41.6px; margin: 1.2em 0 .6em 0; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; text-align: start;\">最小二乘法</h1>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">我们从矩阵的角度来理解：  <br/>\n首先我们给出一个矩阵中的定义： </p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/69FDBBABB65848771BB963D5323410D8' longdesc='__SVG__5dfb536976beede50d2748f52729488e' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='207.49837499999998' height='17.5'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">有了上面的定义之后，我们就可以写出最小二乘问题的矩阵形式：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/8CC825F80F04D1E9FE50922D82ADF843' longdesc='__SVG__14547e766fd680ed7f9d7b87171d494d' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='244.27550000000002' height='26.26365'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">用bi格高一点的说法来说，就是求在欧几里得空间中以2-范数作为距离，使得向量Ax与b之间距离最小的x。  <br/>\n我们的目标是求：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/8A1F52CB18A70FF00FD21A6188673D35' longdesc='__SVG__5024c4cba3348565221213ece877fd22' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='138.33225' height='15.75'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">当然我们知道，使得距离最小的向量x与使得距离平方最小的向量x是相同的，于是我们可以将所求的目标改写为：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/7782F3219A021BA5943C80E349FDC71A' longdesc='__SVG__89443b8a14c697b0c9a629fb545d44f7' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='141.83225' height='19.25'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">结合一些矩阵、行列式的知识，我们知道：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/A6583AB56FE182B28F6BC99A3BFD7040' longdesc='__SVG__a941ed2a4f89a2c692def3d41d91ae35' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='248.65050000000002' height='19.25'></span></span></div></div>\n根据我们大一学过的高数知识，我们知道，求最极值问题直接对应的就是导数为零，因此我们试图将所给出的原式的矩阵形式求导：<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">不过首先我们需要补充矩阵微积分(matrix calculus)的一些知识  <br/>\n(PS:是矩阵微积分吧…我没有翻译错吧….) </p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/A6FB2C7A41451505B17808978A7C0A19' longdesc='__SVG__62aa8a567bfaaefdd34151311da5978d' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='129.56825' height='37.63865'></span></span></div></div>\n<div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/D939D7EEB4FA4B35C805A006F8F49065' longdesc='__SVG__058f610776fee081b40c0b4c9dd7cb67' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='133.95725' height='37.63865'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">如果矩阵A是对称的(symmetric matrix):  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/31FA7B3D1C9A4FAF8246BAAFE66CA054' longdesc='__SVG__9aba38dc3c2cde7e16d8da8aa5b41477' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='112.06825' height='16.625'></span></span></div></div>\n接下来，我们对原式化简并求其对x的导数： <p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/0D7A7E1221948244F73CB01C43E5E2B2' longdesc='__SVG__930091e876fd98d02de46ca5785ba165' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='327.45475' height='19.25'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">求导得到：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/89F88063C60E70AD9A68D1D700C8ED44' longdesc='__SVG__7d053f8fc1c7464104539c36a148f8cc' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='237.27550000000002' height='39.4023'></span></span></div></div><p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">于是我们就得到了，最小二乘法解的矩阵形式：  <br/>\n</p><div  style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><div  style=\"max-width: none; position: relative; width: 100%; text-indent: 0; margin: 1em 0; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; display: block;\"><span  style=\"word-wrap: normal; vertical-align: middle; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin: 0; font-size-adjust: none; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal; padding: 0; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; line-height: 1.6; display: inline-block; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><img src='quiver-image-url/378B7B5D72A1A3C7AFD3DE8D3388FC50' longdesc='__SVG__2b23fcf745364dda1225913495f3ee03' style='border: 0; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;' width='113.81825' height='19.25'></span></span></div></div>\n当然了，这里是最简答的线性最小二乘法，还有更为复杂的非线性以及矩阵A不满秩的情况(hdq说他老师能默写出这个过程…)，等以后有时间了，我会再补充上去的。<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\"/></div><center style='display:none'>%23%u6700%u5C0F%u4E8C%u4E58%u6CD5%0A%0A%u6211%u4EEC%u4ECE%u77E9%u9635%u7684%u89D2%u5EA6%u6765%u7406%u89E3%uFF1A%20%0A%u9996%u5148%u6211%u4EEC%u7ED9%u51FA%u4E00%u4E2A%u77E9%u9635%u4E2D%u7684%u5B9A%u4E49%uFF1A%20%0A%0A%24%24R%28A%29%3D%5C%7BAx%7Cx%u2208R%5En%5C%7D%2CA%u2208R%5E%7Bn%D7n%7D%24%24%0A%0A%u6709%u4E86%u4E0A%u9762%u7684%u5B9A%u4E49%u4E4B%u540E%uFF0C%u6211%u4EEC%u5C31%u53EF%u4EE5%u5199%u51FA%u6700%u5C0F%u4E8C%u4E58%u95EE%u9898%u7684%u77E9%u9635%u5F62%u5F0F%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24%u2203b%u2209R%28A%29%2Cb%u2208R%5En%2C%5Cmin_%7Bx%u2208R%5En%7D%u2225Ax%u2212b%u2225_2%24%24%0A%0A%u7528bi%u683C%u9AD8%u4E00%u70B9%u7684%u8BF4%u6CD5%u6765%u8BF4%uFF0C%u5C31%u662F%u6C42%u5728%u6B27%u51E0%u91CC%u5F97%u7A7A%u95F4%u4E2D%u4EE52-%u8303%u6570%u4F5C%u4E3A%u8DDD%u79BB%uFF0C%u4F7F%u5F97%u5411%u91CFAx%u4E0Eb%u4E4B%u95F4%u8DDD%u79BB%u6700%u5C0F%u7684x%u3002%20%0A%u6211%u4EEC%u7684%u76EE%u6807%u662F%u6C42%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24min_%7Bx%u2208R%5En%7D%u2225Ax%u2212b%u2225_2%24%24%0A%0A%u5F53%u7136%u6211%u4EEC%u77E5%u9053%uFF0C%u4F7F%u5F97%u8DDD%u79BB%u6700%u5C0F%u7684%u5411%u91CFx%u4E0E%u4F7F%u5F97%u8DDD%u79BB%u5E73%u65B9%u6700%u5C0F%u7684%u5411%u91CFx%u662F%u76F8%u540C%u7684%uFF0C%u4E8E%u662F%u6211%u4EEC%u53EF%u4EE5%u5C06%u6240%u6C42%u7684%u76EE%u6807%u6539%u5199%u4E3A%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24min_%7Bx%u2208R%5En%7D%7B%u2225Ax%u2212b%u2225_2%7D%5E2%24%24%0A%0A%u7ED3%u5408%u4E00%u4E9B%u77E9%u9635%u3001%u884C%u5217%u5F0F%u7684%u77E5%u8BC6%uFF0C%u6211%u4EEC%u77E5%u9053%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24%7B%u2225Ax%u2212b%u2225_2%7D%5E2%3D%28Ax%u2212b%29%5ET%u2217%28Ax%u2212b%29%24%24%0A%u6839%u636E%u6211%u4EEC%u5927%u4E00%u5B66%u8FC7%u7684%u9AD8%u6570%u77E5%u8BC6%uFF0C%u6211%u4EEC%u77E5%u9053%uFF0C%u6C42%u6700%u6781%u503C%u95EE%u9898%u76F4%u63A5%u5BF9%u5E94%u7684%u5C31%u662F%u5BFC%u6570%u4E3A%u96F6%uFF0C%u56E0%u6B64%u6211%u4EEC%u8BD5%u56FE%u5C06%u6240%u7ED9%u51FA%u7684%u539F%u5F0F%u7684%u77E9%u9635%u5F62%u5F0F%u6C42%u5BFC%uFF1A%0A%0A%u4E0D%u8FC7%u9996%u5148%u6211%u4EEC%u9700%u8981%u8865%u5145%u77E9%u9635%u5FAE%u79EF%u5206%28matrix%20calculus%29%u7684%u4E00%u4E9B%u77E5%u8BC6%20%0A%28PS%3A%u662F%u77E9%u9635%u5FAE%u79EF%u5206%u5427%u2026%u6211%u6CA1%u6709%u7FFB%u8BD1%u9519%u5427%u2026.%29%20%0A%0A%24%24%5Cfrac%20%7B%5Cpartial%20x%5ETa%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x%7D%3D%5Cfrac%20%7B%5Cpartial%20a%5ETx%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x%7D%3Da%24%24%0A%24%24%5Cfrac%20%7B%5Cpartial%20x%5ETAx%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x%7D%3DAx+A%5ETx%24%24%0A%0A%u5982%u679C%u77E9%u9635A%u662F%u5BF9%u79F0%u7684%28symmetric%20matrix%29%3A%20%0A%24%24Ax+A%5ETx%3D2Ax%24%24%0A%u63A5%u4E0B%u6765%uFF0C%u6211%u4EEC%u5BF9%u539F%u5F0F%u5316%u7B80%u5E76%u6C42%u5176%u5BF9x%u7684%u5BFC%u6570%uFF1A%20%0A%0A%24%24%7B%u2225Ax%u2212b%u2225_2%7D%5E2%3Dx%5ETA%5ETAx%u2212b%5ETAx%u2212x%5ETA%5ETb+b%5ETb%24%24%0A%0A%u6C42%u5BFC%u5F97%u5230%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24%5Cfrac%20%7B%5Cpartial%7B%5Cparallel%20Ax%u2212b%5Cparallel%7D%5E2%7D%7B%5Cpartial%20x%7D%3D2A%5ETAx%u22122A%5ETb%3D0%24%24%0A%0A%u4E8E%u662F%u6211%u4EEC%u5C31%u5F97%u5230%u4E86%uFF0C%u6700%u5C0F%u4E8C%u4E58%u6CD5%u89E3%u7684%u77E9%u9635%u5F62%u5F0F%uFF1A%20%0A%24%24x%3D%28A%5ETA%29%5E%7B%u22121%7DA%5ETb%24%24%0A%u5F53%u7136%u4E86%uFF0C%u8FD9%u91CC%u662F%u6700%u7B80%u7B54%u7684%u7EBF%u6027%u6700%u5C0F%u4E8C%u4E58%u6CD5%uFF0C%u8FD8%u6709%u66F4%u4E3A%u590D%u6742%u7684%u975E%u7EBF%u6027%u4EE5%u53CA%u77E9%u9635A%u4E0D%u6EE1%u79E9%u7684%u60C5%u51B5%28hdq%u8BF4%u4ED6%u8001%u5E08%u80FD%u9ED8%u5199%u51FA%u8FD9%u4E2A%u8FC7%u7A0B%u2026%29%uFF0C%u7B49%u4EE5%u540E%u6709%u65F6%u95F4%u4E86%uFF0C%u6211%u4F1A%u518D%u8865%u5145%u4E0A%u53BB%u7684%u3002%0A%0A%20</center><br/></div>"
